Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:40.10,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.68,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:51.42,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:57.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:04.08,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:07.37,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.50,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats reach the New World at long last,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea, ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's erupting again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there! Who cares about the needles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this? The Transponder Snail is crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?! You have a stomachache?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! That's an emergency signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's calling for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If I pick it up, can we hear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,More than 50 percent of emergency signals are fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My colleagues are getting cut one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The samurai are gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, what's your name?! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody please help me! I'm on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...Punk Hazard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place. The name matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Punk Hazard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were probably not people's houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there were some kind of Government facilities here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Does it actually exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:05:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a mythical creature! There's no way that it's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at those features...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it could be anything else!
