Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be so impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I like how he snarls, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The dragon just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're hearing things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not even sure it's a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's hard to believe but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...it has a lizard-like body with giant wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks exactly how it's described in myths.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He breathed fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This creature is unreal! Am I dreaming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gear 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's well-armored!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's looking at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't provoke him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense your presence-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That dragon just said something!
