Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it too! But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bu! Are you people allies of the Seven Warlords too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seven Warlords?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna breathe fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right above us! We can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep making good desserts for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's change our perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend that you're in a sauna. It feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am breaking out in a super sweat of cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky above the island is divided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One half is burning hot and the other is freezing cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Luffy and the others are not melting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I feel faint...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel lightheaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's heat stroke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...what they call de-cola-ration?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I'm losing it too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot and that dragon said something again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "the Seven Warlords."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have something against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Leave him up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut him up this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me knock him down first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His body is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bu! It's strange but it's cool here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bu! The flames are cool-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, not there! It tickles-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's stuck in the dragon's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What's going on up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the talking voice was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat your own wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure-Kill Green Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Trampolia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One-Sword Style,...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...Draw:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion Song!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This dragon looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can grill it with the fire on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cien Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I made a cold crepe with the Giant Shellfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll pair nicely with champagne...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Are they sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fog?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I inhaled too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The gas made them sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a natural phenomenon, indigenous to the New World?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did somebody sneak into the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope those four
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that went to the island took a Baby Transponder Snail with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to let them know... somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.78,0:22:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Two humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...one cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And their pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tie them all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good that they're pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will care if they go missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:23:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take them to the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.50,0:23:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and crew have saved someone from the dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are extremely shocked when they see his bizarre appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.40,0:23:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Sanji and the others have been captured by someone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and are locked in a mysterious room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is there that they see an unbelievable sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Straw Hats Astonished!\NEnter the Puzzling Samurai's Head!"
Dialogue: 2,0:23:30.35,0:23:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
